---
import Greeting from "@/components/home/Greeting.astro"
---

<section class="home-intro" aria-labelledby="home-greeting">
  <Greeting />
  <prose-content>
    <p>I'm Viet. 👋</p>
    <p>
      I build industrial robotics 🤖 and manufacturing systems—real-world
      automation that powers modern factories.
    </p>
    <p>
      Previously, I worked in banking and finance, focused on corporate lending
      and capital financing.
    </p>
    <p>
      You'll also likely find me waitering tables and talking to random
      strangers at
      <a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/RCQeb1NXjn82n1jn9">Ai Izakaya</a>
      or
      <a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/MLYB2SFwL4q8vgww8">Sake Labo</a>.
    </p>
    <p>
      In my free time, I read about business, economics, technology, history,
      and politics. I also enjoy travel, good food & drink, great coffee, and
      learning about different cultures.
    </p>
    <p>
      This is my personal experimental playground for exploring ideas,
      obsessions, and the occasional rabbit 🐰 holes.
    </p>
  </prose-content>
</section>

<style>
  .home-intro {
    @media (width >= 64rem) {
      margin-block-start: -0.2em;
    }
  }
</style>
